humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The pathology report does not provide information on the number of positive lymph nodes or the presence of metastatic carcinoma in regional or sentinel lymph nodes. Based on the new rules 10 and 11, N0 can indicate no metastatic carcinoma in sentinel lymph nodes and regional lymph nodes or that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage for this patient is N0.
